  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A quirky cooperative puzzle game that can be played with friends and online players. Fluffy cube-shaped creatures team up to solve puzzles together!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Local and Online Co-op Multiplayer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ring the bell</strong> in the lobby to match with other players online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/458bcf4794f8a1635cb784918dd0e99c.poster.avif?t=1746668625\" width=800 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/458bcf4794f8a1635cb784918dd0e99c.webm?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/458bcf4794f8a1635cb784918dd0e99c.mp4?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play locally or create a <strong>party code</strong> with the TV in the lobby, so <strong>friends can join you</strong> online. Play in any combination e.g. two local players and two online players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/09b08672c263b7ba7dfd02ac71f936d2.poster.avif?t=1746668625\" width=800 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/09b08672c263b7ba7dfd02ac71f936d2.webm?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/09b08672c263b7ba7dfd02ac71f936d2.mp4?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Duo Mode</strong> allows you to control 2 creatures from 1 controller. Share the controller with a friend to use half each or test your skills to control both yourself!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/e57ef64b60aa48567a8dfd54af54e3ad.avif?t=1746668625\" width=602 height=333 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Helping Each Other is Key, for All Ages</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With <strong>intuitive and simple controls</strong>, anyone can jump into the game right away. Since you can’t rotate, solving puzzles always requires the help of your friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/1db649b8a66cc2cb488a1a57dbb55eaf.poster.avif?t=1746668625\" width=800 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/1db649b8a66cc2cb488a1a57dbb55eaf.webm?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/1db649b8a66cc2cb488a1a57dbb55eaf.mp4?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>160 Diverse Stages, Including Special Stages</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stages usually require all players to work together but every now and then a <strong>special 2v2 stage</strong> appears!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/5e6c08595bfd7ab973b327b733a95b2b.poster.avif?t=1746668625\" width=800 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/5e6c08595bfd7ab973b327b733a95b2b.webm?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/5e6c08595bfd7ab973b327b733a95b2b.mp4?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Spin the gacha to get stamps</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use coins to spin the gacha. <strong>Collect stamps</strong> and unlock accessories and furniture. Once you’ve collected enough stamps you’ll unlock new items and <strong>stage themes</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/ee85c2edfe63a841978278026a27bbec.avif?t=1746668625\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras_big/ee85c2edfe63a841978278026a27bbec.avif?t=1746668625 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize with Accessories, Skins and Furniture</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Change the furniture to create your own <strong>unique room</strong>, also change your character's skin and accessories to <strong>suit your style!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/607368866c01b4cbd57b1fdd2ef85059.poster.avif?t=1746668625\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/607368866c01b4cbd57b1fdd2ef85059.webm?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/607368866c01b4cbd57b1fdd2ef85059.mp4?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fun Voice Feature</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With simple controls, the creatures will <strong>say various phrases</strong> depending on the situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/ce0f950743092b3e82b3b4082f11b894.poster.avif?t=1746668625\" width=800 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/ce0f950743092b3e82b3b4082f11b894.webm?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/ce0f950743092b3e82b3b4082f11b894.mp4?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
