314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/5e6c08595bfd7ab973b327b733a95b2b.webm?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/5e6c08595bfd7ab973b327b733a95b2b.mp4?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Spin the gacha to get stamps</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use coins to spin the gacha. <strong>Collect stamps</strong> and unlock accessories and furniture. Once you’ve collected enough stamps you’ll unlock new items and <strong>stage themes</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/ee85c2edfe63a841978278026a27bbec.avif?t=1746668625\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras_big/ee85c2edfe63a841978278026a27bbec.avif?t=1746668625 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize with Accessories, Skins and Furniture</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Change the furniture to create your own <strong>unique room</strong>, also change your character's skin and accessories to <strong>suit your style!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/607368866c01b4cbd57b1fdd2ef85059.poster.avif?t=1746668625\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/607368866c01b4cbd57b1fdd2ef85059.webm?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/607368866c01b4cbd57b1fdd2ef8505